Road.

25
00:01:14,549 --> 00:01:18,130
The Belt and Road Initiative is the massive
infrastructure plan

26
00:01:18,130 --> 00:01:21,529
to build trade corridors between China and
the rest of the world.

27
00:01:21,529 --> 00:01:23,680
It’s also known as One Belt,

28
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:26,299
One Reason to Not Go into Debt.

29
00:01:26,299 --> 00:01:29,670
That’s because it has been a convenient
way

30
00:01:29,670 --> 00:01:32,999
for the Chinese regime to saddle some small
countries

31
00:01:32,999 --> 00:01:35,979
with debt they can't pay back.

32
00:01:35,979 --> 00:01:37,380
So in exchange,

33
00:01:37,380 --> 00:01:39,149
these countries have to sign over

34
00:01:39,149 --> 00:01:42,880
valuable resources or assets to China.

35
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:47,179
The poster child for this is of course, Sri
Lanka.

36
00:01:47,179 --> 00:01:48,549
When you can go from sun-kissed

37
00:01:48,549 --> 00:01:51,979
to mountain mists in only four hours,

38
00:01:51,979 --> 00:01:53,819
that’s so Sri Lanka.

39
00:01:53,819 --> 00:01:56,399
When dolphins and whales swim around you all
year,

40
00:01:56,399 --> 00:01:59,989
so you can visit them at any time?

41
00:01:59,989 --> 00:02:01,789
That’s so Sri Lanka.

42
00:02:01,789 --> 00:02:03,779
And when you take a giant Chinese loan

43
00:02:03,779 --> 00:02:05,579
to build a deep water port,

44
00:02:05,579 --> 00:02:07,619
can’t pay the loan back,

45
00:02:07,620 --> 00:02:11,220
and then have to give the port to China on
a 99-year lease,

46
00:02:11,220 --> 00:02:13,610
that’s so Sri Lanka.

47
00:02:13,610 --> 00:02:15,030
The list of countries at risk

48
00:02:15,030 --> 00:02:18,180
of falling into China's debt trap is long.

49
00:02:18,180 --> 00:02:20,800
It includes places like Djibouti

50
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:21,800
Kenya

51
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:22,800
Pakistan.

52
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:25,330
And it looked like Malaysia, too…

53
00:02:25,330 --> 00:02:29,000
But then came Malaysian Prime Minister Mahathir
Mohamad.

54
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:31,700
After taking office in 2018,

55
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:36,140
