worth of

56
00:02:36,140 --> 00:02:38,810
China-backed infrastructure deals.

57
00:02:38,810 --> 00:02:42,670
He also scrapped three China-backed pipeline
projects

58
00:02:42,670 --> 00:02:45,280
worth 3 billion dollars.

59
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:47,260
And there was also a railway project

60
00:02:47,260 --> 00:02:49,760
called the East Coast Rail Link.

61
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:50,940
It was supposed to be built by

62
00:02:50,940 --> 00:02:54,210
China Communications Construction Company—

63
00:02:54,210 --> 00:02:58,980
for a price tag of nearly 20 billion dollars.

64
00:02:58,980 --> 00:03:01,520
He scrapped that, too.

65
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,960
But he still wanted some of the infrastructure.

66
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,780
Just not at that price.

67
00:03:05,780 --> 00:03:09,940
So he re-negotiated the price of the East
Coast Rail Link—

68
00:03:09,940 --> 00:03:15,130
